comments: Mobley (CLE) establishes himself in Harris' (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Reed (PHI) backs into Mobley (CLE), initiating contact with his lower body that prevents him from getting to the pass.
Maxey (PHI) brings his left arm to Garland's (CLE) side as he makes a move to the basket and the contact is marginal.
Allen (CLE) establishes himself in Maxey's (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Mobley (CLE) steps out of bounds while in possession of the ball.
Allen (CLE) never establishes himself in a screening position in Oubre Jr.'s (PHI) path, as he continues forwards into him and delivers contact.
Garland (CLE) legally contests Hield's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Maxey (PHI) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Garland (CLE) and is not in a legal guarding position when contact occurs during Garland's upward shooting motion.
Hield (PHI) brushes Strus's (CLE) arm and marginal contact occurs during the shot attempt near the rim.
Okoro (CLE) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
Mobley (CLE) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
